OL,3,CTourette's syndrome campaigner from
OL,4,CScottish Borders inspires new film
OL,6,FA man from the Scottish Borders says
OL,7,Fhe is "humbled" to have his story
OL,8,Fadapted for the silver screen.
OL,10,FJohn Davidson, from Galashiels, has
OL,11,Flived with Tourette's syndrome for
OL,12,Fmost of his life, a condition that
OL,13,Fcauses involuntary ticks and urges to
OL,14,Fshout and swear.
OL,16,FJohn has starred in many documentaries
OL,17,Fthroughout the years and has earned an
OL,18,FMBE for his campaigning to raise more
OL,19,Fawareness of his condition.
