OL,3,CTourette's syndrome campaigner from
OL,4,CScottish Borders inspires new film
OL,6,FHis story has now been used as the
OL,7,Finspiration for a new biopic film,
OL,8,Fwhich he says he hopes will open new
OL,9,Fconversations.
OL,11,FThe film, 'I Swear', is a comedy-drama
OL,12,Fabout John's life and the struggles he
OL,13,Ffaced growing up with Tourette's
OL,14,Fsyndrome in the 1980s, when awareness
OL,15,Fand understanding around the condition
OL,16,Fwas lacking.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/5
