OL,3,CTourette's syndrome campaigner from
OL,4,CScottish Borders inspires new film
OL,6,F"To sit and watch it on screen was
OL,7,Fabsolutely unreal. It just felt very
OL,8,Fhumbling and very thankful that at
OL,9,Flast we're managing to get the right
OL,10,Finformation out", says John.
OL,12,F"It's so good to get it across the way
OL,13,Fwe've got it across in the film
OL,14,Fbecause it's given people a real sense
OL,15,Fof what it must be like for me to live
OL,16,Fwith".
OL,18,FJohn's character is played by Robert
OL,19,FAramayo, who says he spent a lot of
OL,20,Ftime in Galashiels with John ahead of
OL,21,Ffilming.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/5
