OL,3,CTourette's syndrome campaigner from
OL,4,CScottish Borders inspires new film
OL,6,F"I think about him walking along the
OL,7,Friver with his dog and that amazing
OL,8,Flandscape around Galashiels and the
OL,9,FBorders, so it was really important
OL,10,Fand really informative, in terms of
OL,11,Fbuilding out a more three dimensional
OL,12,Fversion of him", says the actor.
OL,14,FThe film is directed by Kirk Jones,
OL,15,Fwho said: "For me as writer and
OL,16,Fdirector, two of the most interesting
OL,17,Fand powerful elements are comedy and
OL,18,Femotion. And I felt like I could
OL,19,Fidentify both of those in John's story.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/5
