OL,3,CTourette's syndrome campaigner from
OL,4,CScottish Borders inspires new film
OL,6,F"And when I finally got to meet him I
OL,7,Fsaid 'If I said to you I feel like I
OL,8,Fcan identify a level of comedy in this
OL,9,Fcondition, would that upset you? Would
OL,10,Fit anger you?' and he said 'No, my
OL,11,Flife has been the funniest and at
OL,12,Ftimes the most tragic you can ever
OL,13,Fimagine'."
